{
  "stem": "26609.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I mentioned before that the Russians took my husband because he was an engineer, and they needed him in the wartime.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since then, I haven't seen him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was left alone with a very young-- it was actually a baby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] never heard anything more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a Pole who lived on the same-- mostly Ukrainians, and some Poles, lived opposite.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he knew me and my husband-- a young man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He came back from-- when the Germans were-- the beginning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Actually the Germans were not-- that was the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not in Lwow, they were in Przemysl, not far from Lwow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And otherwise he wouldn't come over, and he wouldn't know that I am alive there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came over-- on the street, actually, I have seen him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I have seen your husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were both [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When the Russians came forward [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to Lwow, he was with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they went over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They pushed out the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's why they came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Later they came back, the Germans came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they caught-- I don't know-- a division or how many-- the Germans, not far from Tarnopol-- that was before Lwow-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] about, I don't know, a whole division of Russians.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Germans took over-- took them with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they went in a transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They put somewhere-- I don't know where, exactly-- but past Lwow, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my husband wanted-- he has seen it-- he says.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know to believe him or not-- that he has seen that my husband wanted to jump out from a train in motion.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He thought that no one will see him jump out.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
